cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.SD, cs.CL, cs.GR 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with real-time lip sync for 2D characters, which involves image processing and analysis. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is also likely as the paper deals with audio and visual data for animation. 
- cs.SD (Software Engineering) is a possibility as the paper describes the development of a deep learning-based interactive system. 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is a possibility as the paper deals with natural language processing for generating lip sync. 
- cs.GR (Graphics) is a possibility as the paper deals with 2D animation and character design.
